<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>每日运动科学文献简报 | {{ date }}</title>
  <style>
    body {
      max-width: 920px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      padding: 0 20px;
      color: #202124;
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", "Noto Sans SC", sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.75;
      background: #ffffff;
    }
    h1 { font-size: 30px; line-height: 1.35; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    h2 { font-size: 22px; line-height: 1.4; margin: 0 0 12px; }
    .overview {
      border: 1px solid #d0d7de;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 18px 20px;
      background: #f6f8fa;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }
    .paper-card {
      border: 1px solid #d0d7de;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 22px 24px;
      margin: 24px 0;
    }
    .meta { color: #57606a; margin: 6px 0; }
    .journal-metrics {
      border: 1px solid #d8dee4;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 12px 14px;
      margin: 14px 0;
      background: #fbfbfd;
    }
    .journal-metrics ul { margin: 6px 0 0 18px; padding: 0; }
    .score { font-weight: 700; }
    .field { margin: 18px 0; }
    .label { font-weight: 700; }
    .evidence {
      border-left: 4px solid #0969da;
      background: #f6f8fa;
      padding: 10px 14px;
      margin: 18px 0;
      color: #24292f;
    }
    .dict {
      border-top: 1px solid #d0d7de;
      margin-top: 34px;
      padding-top: 18px;
    }
    a { color: #0969da; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>每日运动科学文献简报 | {{ date }}</h1>

  <section class="overview">
    <h2>今日概览</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>检索范围：{{ overview.start_date }} 至 {{ overview.end_date }}</li>
      <li>初筛文章：{{ overview.fetched_count }} 篇</li>
      <li>最终推荐：{{ overview.selected_count }} 篇</li>
      <li>本期重点方向：{{ overview.focus_topics }}</li>
      {% if overview.top_pick.index %}
      <li>今日最值得读：第 {{ overview.top_pick.index }} 篇，{{ overview.top_pick.reason }}</li>
      {% else %}
      <li>今日最值得读：{{ overview.top_pick.reason }}</li>
      {% endif %}
    </ul>
  </section>

  {% if metadata.dry_run %}
  <p class="evidence">dry-run：本次不会更新 <code>data/seen_papers.json</code>。</p>
  {% endif %}
  {% if metadata.warnings %}
  <p class="evidence">运行提示：部分外部数据源补全失败，不影响已生成内容；详见命令行 warning。</p>
  {% endif %}

  {% if not papers %}
  <p>今天没有达到评分阈值的新增文章。</p>
  <p>这不代表相关领域没有新文献，只表示在当前期刊白名单、关键词和评分阈值下没有入选。</p>
  {% endif %}

  {% for paper in papers %}
  <article class="paper-card">
    <h2>{{ loop.index }}. {{ paper.chinese_title }}</h2>
    <p class="meta"><strong>英文原题：</strong>{{ paper.title }}</p>
    <p class="meta"><strong>期刊 / 年份 / DOI / PMID：</strong>{{ paper.journal }} / {{ paper.year }} / {{ paper.doi }} / {{ paper.pmid }}</p>
    <section class="journal-metrics">
      <strong>期刊信息</strong>
      <ul>
        <li>期刊：{{ paper.journal_metrics.display_name }}</li>
        <li>影响因子：{{ paper.journal_metrics.impact_factor_display }}</li>
        <li>JCR分区：{{ paper.journal_metrics.jcr_display }}</li>
        <li>中科院分区：{{ paper.journal_metrics.cas_display }}</li>
        <li>指标年份：{{ paper.journal_metrics.metrics_year_display }}</li>
        <li>数据来源：{{ paper.journal_metrics.metrics_source }}</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
    <p class="meta"><strong>文章类型：</strong>{{ paper.article_type_label }}</p>
    <p class="meta"><strong>本篇方向：</strong>{{ paper.direction_display }}</p>
    <p class="meta"><strong>研究类型标签：</strong>{{ paper.study_type_display }}</p>
    <p class="meta"><strong>数据来源：</strong>{{ paper.data_source_display }}</p>
    <p class="meta"><strong>是否顶刊雷达：</strong>{{ paper.elite_radar_display }}</p>
    <p class="field"><span class="label">和我有什么关系：</span>{{ paper.relation_to_me }}</p>
    <p class="score">推荐指数：{{ paper.stars }}（{{ paper.recommendation_index }}） | 质量评分：{{ paper.score }}/100</p>
    <p class="meta"><strong>关键词：</strong>{{ paper.keywords_display }}</p>
    <p class="meta"><strong>链接：</strong><a href="{{ paper.link }}">{{ paper.link }}</a></p>
    <p class="evidence"><strong>证据强度提醒：</strong>{{ paper.evidence_strength }}</p>

    {% for section in paper.body_sections %}
    <p class="field"><span class="label">{{ section.label }}：</span>{{ section.value }}</p>
    {% endfor %}
  </article>
  {% endfor %}

  <section class="dict">
    <h2>今日术语小词典</h2>
    {% if term_dictionary %}
    <ul>
      {% for item in term_dictionary %}
      <li><strong>{{ item.term }}</strong>：{{ item.definition }}</li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
    {% else %}
    <p>今天入选文章没有触发需要额外解释的英文缩写或术语。</p>
    {% endif %}
  </section>

  <p class="meta">生成时间：{{ generated_at }}</p>
</body>
</html>
